Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}CP, this is Alpha 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing unusual to report at Point 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alpha 2, this is CP.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continue your observation mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency Kaiju alert. Emergency Kaiju alert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An emergency Kaiju alert\Nhas just been issued. I repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency Kaiju Alert
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An emergency Kaiju alert\Nhas been issued for the South, Central,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokohama Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency Evacuation Shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm and head for the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Isogo wards in Yokohama City,\NKanagawa Prefecture.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Citizens in the designated areas are\Nto seek refuge in a shelter immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The epicenter's projected route is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target is currently en route\Nfrom Yatobashi to Yamashita-cho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its estimated body length is 60 meters.\NFortitude 3.5. Over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.85,0:02:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one on thermals\Nwithin a 3 kilometer radius.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All units, open fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat. Open fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger. Luring target to the TO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Special\NKaiju Alert
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiju Alert in\NYokohama City
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we succeed in getting its attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Which division will come, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this is Yokohama,\Nit'll be the Third Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, they got its guts over {\i1}everything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be overtime\Nfor me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cut through this!\NThe fat's jamming the saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me the heat chainsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't start lifting that yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Bring a stretcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It only got on your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it happen to me a bunch of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you file for workers' comp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Things always get messy\Nwhen the Third Division's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to tell what's organs and what's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway... do they really expect us\Nto finish this by the end of the week?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka, got a new job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an opening elsewhere on-site.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got permission from management.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still smell it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, tonight's feature story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, the Kaiju that appeared\Nin Yokohama was defeated{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}thanks to the heroic efforts of\Nthe Defense Force's Third Division.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Division Greeted With Cheers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:06:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Report: The Third Division
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:06:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the division's leader is none\Nother than the famous Captain Mina Ashiro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain     Mina Ashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only is she captain\Nat the young age of 27,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she's also defeated several hundred Kaiju.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An Up-Close Look at The Third Division
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Report: The Third Division
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain               Mina Ashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wipe out all the Kaiju together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Report: The Third Division
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain        Mina Ashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her cool, elegant demeanor makes her\Nthe most popular of all the division captains!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say she's in the running\Nto be corps commander, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Report: The Third Division
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Future                 Corps Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's definitely one to keep an eye on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd I wind up on this side of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kafka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a new part-timer starting today.\NThis is Ichikawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he's aiming\Nto join the Defense Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was once like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave up, though, and now\Nhe's part of the furniture here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, this sucks...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Toku-san... You're freaking the new kid out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I did do my best, you know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how good you are,\Nthere's always somebody better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say I reached\Nthe limit of how far I could go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'll never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I won't know until the day I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I'd even want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I thought you\Nand him would get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing I could've said\Nthat wouldn't make me sound like a loser!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is giving up that bad?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miike's team can stay on bone cleaning duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the important ones ready for Izumo Tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshimura's team can start\Ntaking apart the legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dump all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,New kid, you're on intestines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hah! That's what you get!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Kafka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good with intestine work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Fine, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He complains, but he never says no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He would've done a great job\Nin the Defense Force if he'd passed the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, he's definitely feeling it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so am I.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}Tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that lunch box all the food you brought?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel up to eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}Multivitamin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get {\i1}something{\i0} in your stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or you won't last the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And these. You can have these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These help a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what you're saying,\Nbut I really don't need those.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit playing coy and put them in your nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Senpai, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everybody's like\Nthat their first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all responsible\Nfor carrying your own stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least the smelliest\Npart of the job is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did you come to get back\Nat me for what I did at lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I made\Nit through my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're raising the age limit to 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For applicants to the Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough young people anymore, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you what to do\Nwith your life, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you talked about\Ngiving up, you looked so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I really don't care at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I'm wrong, you can just give up\Nand I won't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lot nicer than I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I really don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpa—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Yoju?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get as far away from here as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're sure you're safe, call it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fight this thing alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Another body won't make any difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to join the Defense Force, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So why would you let\Nyourself get killed here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! I'm the one you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it can't follow me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your place, my place, our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for this, Kaiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to beating {\i1}Guramon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what you're sad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad that Miiko died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miiko, your calico cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to join the Defense Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}Kafka has arrived!\NMina has arrived!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dumb. You're just a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For Miiko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in elementary school too, Kafka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who can be\Na cooler Defense Force officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wipe out all the Kaiju together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it all! It wasn't supposed to be like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ain't afraid of you, Kaiju!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aim for the leg...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aim...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I called it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I left you to die here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never make it in the Defense Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}Application Result{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}Mr. Kafka Hibino{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}We regret to inform you that you have not passed\Nthe first round of the recently concluded\NAnti-Kaiju Defense Force selection tests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-Kaiju Defense Force
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Accepting Applicants
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so powerless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing's changed at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't protect anything.\NNot my game console, or my friend's cat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or even the new kid at my job!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Target down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiating rescue operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Igarashi. Takaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll check the area for any other Yoju.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move. Just stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mina's incredible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She took down that scary\Nthing in less than a second...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's left me in the dust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When that Kaiju showed up\Nand you told me to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't saved my life then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've died today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who can be\Na cooler Defense Force officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should think\Nabout joining the Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's your call. Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't just keep running forever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anything\Nwrong with giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not good to lie to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give\Nthe Defense Force another go—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kai... A Kai—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your wounds bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAAAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa! It's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't freak out like that, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! We can show him\Nit's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, give him a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! A smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's definitely not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gramps, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, like, totally a Kaiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that? An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Defense Force is probably on their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you encounter a Kaiju,\Nthe first thing you do is target the legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You bind it so it can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a little scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When I imagine fighting a Kaiju\Nthat's so much bigger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you get scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be right by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaiju has appeared at\NYokohama South General Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get my team ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll eliminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A small Kaiju has appeared within Yokohama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat. A small Kaiju\Nhas appeared within Yokohama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiju is fleeing from\NYokohama South General Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading for an evacuated area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a cordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're inside, there'll be nobody around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Defense Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's coming from underground...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Car 2, maintain course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head to the new location.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same type\Nas the one that attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, they already started evacuating\Nwhen the alert was sent out about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just pray there'll be no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Run... quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait! I'll get you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Run... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I'm really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course. Sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Got it! I'll be gone\Nin a moment! So don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just unconscious. She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa, get them out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna try...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Punching it as hard as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.40,0:24:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.56,0:24:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,definitely can't do that to a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.06,0:25:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.40,0:25:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing Based on Witness Testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaiju No. 8.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.15,0:25:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the eighth Kaiju that\Nthe Defense Force has given a codename.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.23,0:25:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiju No. 8\N(Witness Composite)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.81,0:25:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They still haven't found this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.65,0:25:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. 8 remains at large, with\Nthe Defense Force actively searching for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.48,0:25:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This has gotten way out of hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.27,0:25:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Male Eyewitness (103)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.69,0:25:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been three months.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.27,0:25:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai became the first Kaiju in history\Nto escape the Defense Force,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.52,0:25:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Male Eyewitness (103)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.52,0:25:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret World of Cryptids
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and every Defense Force officer\Nin the country is looking for him now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.35,0:25:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.56,0:26:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Kafka got something in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.90,0:26:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Application Result
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.15,0:26:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are pleased to inform you that you have passed the first round\Nof the recently concluded Anti-Kaiju Defense Force selection tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.81,0:26:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.35,0:26:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.65,0:26:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.77,0:26:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Defense Force's\NTachikawa Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Kumagaya Base on\Na field trip once, but this one's way bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.02,0:26:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They share this area\Nwith a Self-Defense Forces garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.85,0:26:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When something happens,\Nboth sides work together
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.56,0:26:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to dispatch troops all over western Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.77,0:26:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you transformed here,\Nyou'd be dead within seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.98,0:26:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in getting scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.69,0:26:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.94,0:26:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.56,0:26:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a little early,\Nbut let's get checked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.60,0:26:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.23,0:26:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.19,0:26:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.06,0:26:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.69,0:27:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.06,0:27:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.02,0:27:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That rust bucket is yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.52,0:27:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.90,0:27:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't park my car, so move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.65,0:27:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's tons of open spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.69,0:27:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to park it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.85,0:27:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My lucky number today is five.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.56,0:27:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lucky number?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.94,0:27:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with this little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.90,0:27:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.27,0:27:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This young man is going to\Nteach you a lesson in manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.56,0:27:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll move it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.02,0:27:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.81,0:27:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That suit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.60,0:27:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monster Sweeper, Inc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.81,0:28:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The company car!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.90,0:28:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.52,0:28:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Examinee number 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.90,0:28:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My hobby is murdering Kaiju.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.31,0:28:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.40,0:28:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinomiya? That last name...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.81,0:28:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.52,0:28:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know you smell like a Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.81,0:28:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the applicants this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.10,0:28:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot look pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.35,0:28:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What the hell is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.69,0:28:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't keep up at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.23,0:28:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd been keeping up my training out of habit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.06,0:29:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I do really hard\Nphysical work every day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.85,0:29:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before, I used to be just below average!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.81,0:29:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.94,0:29:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you really get this weak\Nwhen you turn thirty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.19,0:29:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it... My body doesn't want to move at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.77,0:29:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino\NFitness Exam Rank
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.60,0:29:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,219 out of 225
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.06,0:29:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.90,0:29:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't use\Nyour Kaiju power, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.02,0:29:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's put\Nin a lot of effort to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.85,0:29:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be fair to use my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.35,0:29:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be so cool\Nto say that, but I should've used it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.06,0:29:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages since I last tried this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.81,0:29:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.65,0:29:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bet it all on the next part!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.56,0:29:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Area 2
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.15,0:29:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.19,0:29:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.52,0:29:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Third Division Vice-Captain Hoshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.31,0:29:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the head of the second\Nstage exam committee this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.69,0:30:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be doing your aptitude test\Nhere in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.15,0:30:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your task in this area will be\Nto find Kaiju and...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.48,0:30:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutralize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't send you in empty-handed,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.48,0:30:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll be wearing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.85,0:30:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.81,0:30:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.44,0:30:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pressing itself up against my body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.60,0:30:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start measuring the unleashed combat power\Nof the ones who have their suits on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reno Ichikawa. Unleashed combat power, 8%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.27,0:30:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruichi Izumo, 18%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.56,0:30:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aoi Kaguragi, 15%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.40,0:30:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iharu Furuhashi, 14%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.85,0:31:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.06,0:31:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lucky to get one\Napplicant a year above 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This year might be a bumper crop\Nlike we've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.19,0:31:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.23,0:31:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unleashed combat power, 46%!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.06,0:31:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa. She's already at the level\Nof a platoon leader.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.15,0:31:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be a record for anybody\Nwho hasn't officially joined yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.52,0:31:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 8%...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.98,0:31:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, there's no reason\Nto get down, Ichikawa-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.94,0:31:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, if you don't have a zero\Nat this point, you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.48,0:31:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've never even seen a zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.56,0:31:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grr!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.02,0:31:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.98,0:31:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unleashed combat power, 0%!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.85,0:31:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.19,0:31:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's my first zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are the measurements wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.35,0:31:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a little more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.56,0:31:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to squeeze it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.48,0:31:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not trying to take a dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.15,0:31:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't squeeze it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.73,0:32:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.60,0:32:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! There's got to be some trick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to figure it out\Nbefore the exam ends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.27,0:32:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Defense Force Screening Exam Final Test
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.77,0:32:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll explain the test.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.56,0:32:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your targets are a Honju and 36 Yoju{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.77,0:32:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that have been placed throughout\Nthe urban training area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.85,0:32:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These Kaiju caused sixteen\Nfatalities in Hachioji last year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.60,0:32:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We captured them alive\Nto serve as training aids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.56,0:32:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're going to fight them\Nwith anti-Kaiju weapons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.81,0:32:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll all be tracked with a drone\Nthat will monitor your actions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.15,0:32:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we decide your life is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.27,0:32:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll remotely activate\Nthe shield on your suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.44,0:32:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but be aware this will mean you fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.65,0:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest, I can't guarantee\Nyou'll survive this next part.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.02,0:33:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if you're willing\Nto accept that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.77,0:33:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.02,0:33:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.48,0:33:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoju 12 down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.27,0:33:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoju 03 down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.44,0:33:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.02,0:33:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Let's get going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.98,0:33:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind, Ichikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.10,0:33:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.90,0:33:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This equipment is incredibly heavy\Nwithout the suit helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.15,0:33:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I, the zero, can understand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.73,0:33:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.27,0:33:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I forgot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.40,0:33:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Mina Ashiro is here\Nfor the test as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.69,0:33:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to look good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.81,0:33:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.40,0:34:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who cares if I'm a zero?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.27,0:34:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down. This is your last chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.02,0:34:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.15,0:34:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the examining officers\Nfollowing us all with drones?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.19,0:34:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,True... If all they cared about\Nwas how many Kaiju you killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.81,0:34:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they could just track\Nthat number with sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.31,0:34:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.73,0:34:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're testing our abilities,\Nbut also how we can adapt to the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.69,0:34:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means since we lack that kind of\Noffensive capability, we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.40,0:34:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.60,0:34:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Support all the attackers as best we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.98,0:34:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.10,0:34:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those hooves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.60,0:34:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know this guy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.52,0:34:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one we did a joint\Ndisposal of with Iida Cleaners!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.06,0:35:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's why they included\Nthese in our equipment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.44,0:35:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.40,0:35:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A stun grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.10,0:35:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got weak eyesight\Nbut incredibly good hearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've deafened them,\Nthey're easy targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.10,0:35:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.81,0:35:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The skin on its stomach\Nis weaker than most Kaiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.19,0:35:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.65,0:35:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.02,0:35:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.60,0:35:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've taken apart more\NKaiju bodies than we can count!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.40,0:35:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you guys inside and out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.19,0:35:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.94,0:36:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.60,0:36:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.40,0:36:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.94,0:36:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Area Delta, Number 2032 injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.90,0:36:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Irregularities detected in vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.69,0:36:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoju 23 is continuing to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.77,0:36:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the remote shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.35,0:36:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.77,0:36:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stand up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.15,0:36:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.60,0:36:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's watching!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.15,0:36:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Figured he'd be the first to drop out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.65,0:36:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was a funny guy... Too bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.69,0:36:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Activating remote shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.02,0:37:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm on the battlefield,\Nnobody gets to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.65,0:37:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.31,0:37:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go defeat them,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.60,0:37:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so you just lie on the ground like a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.65,0:37:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going after the main target?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.02,0:37:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Better pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so much more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.15,0:37:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really the same equipment we've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.31,0:37:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So your unleashed combat power makes\Nthat much of a difference, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.02,0:37:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.90,0:37:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.02,0:37:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's broken?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.65,0:37:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stand up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.73,0:37:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}2032, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Hoshina in the operation room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.73,0:37:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're seeing irregularities in your vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.52,0:37:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple fractures, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.81,0:38:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly organ damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.52,0:38:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.52,0:38:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As the exam proctor,\NI recommend you drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those shields aren't perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.94,0:38:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who decides if I give up or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.44,0:38:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.90,0:38:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too old for dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.10,0:38:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I look like an idiot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.27,0:38:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to bet my\Nwhole life up to this point
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.31,0:38:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and chase my dreams again!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.56,0:38:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.81,0:38:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm not giving up, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.10,0:39:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these guys for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.77,0:39:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ichikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.31,0:39:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By our powers combined!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.56,0:39:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's staring at me,\Nand I'm really embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.06,0:39:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow Kikoru and don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.23,0:39:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.35,0:39:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.56,0:39:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so damn fast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.10,0:39:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not even letting us help her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.27,0:40:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 2016 has taken down\Nthe last Yoju in Area Delta,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and is now engaging the Honju!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.65,0:40:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.19,0:40:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Honju has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.02,0:40:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final stage of the exam is complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.27,0:40:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recovering drones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.98,0:40:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good work, everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.40,0:41:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is just too goddamn fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.15,0:41:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Combination
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.73,0:41:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Undone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.77,0:41:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru Shinomiya's even more\Npowerful than the rumors say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.23,0:41:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she's enough to catch even your eye, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.90,0:41:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd imagined we'd see\Nabout thirty people drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.85,0:41:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.15,0:41:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And with only minimal injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.19,0:41:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's clearly all thanks to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you'd expect to see\Nfrom Director Shinomiya's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.27,0:41:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be a big shot in the Defense Force\Nsomeday, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.69,0:41:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And a ray of hope for this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.60,0:41:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was perfect, wasn't I, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.40,0:42:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, time to go back and laugh\Nat Kafka Hibino a fourth time...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.69,0:42:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru Shinomiya was every bit\Nthe monster everybody said she was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.27,0:42:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to her, we made it to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.27,0:42:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just wait for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.73,0:42:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.48,0:42:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.81,0:42:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.19,0:42:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.44,0:42:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.60,0:42:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. I'll let you handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.81,0:42:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can {\i0}talk{\i1}?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.65,0:42:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.81,0:42:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.19,0:42:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.15,0:43:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you chew before you swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.56,0:43:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.90,0:43:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Abnormalities detected in 2016's vitals!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.02,0:43:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What's happening out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.44,0:43:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.81,0:43:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're picking up live signals\Nfrom the Kaiju they already killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.19,0:43:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.44,0:43:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Kaiju shouldn't be able to\Ncome back to life like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.35,0:43:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an estimated fortitude\Nfor the revived Honju!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.77,0:43:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 6.4!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.35,0:43:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more powerful now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.44,0:43:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshina, we're heading out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.52,0:43:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.35,0:43:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency. Emergency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.60,0:43:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Examinees are to immediately\Nevacuate to the nearest shelter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.98,0:43:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I say again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.27,0:43:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evacuate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.81,0:43:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't evacuate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.69,0:43:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If somebody doesn't stop this thing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.15,0:43:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lots of people will die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.69,0:44:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can still move. I can still fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.31,0:44:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I'm on the battlefield...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.31,0:44:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody dies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.77,0:44:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Be perfect, for the sake\Nof this nation's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.77,0:44:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.60,0:44:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Honju sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.02,0:44:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru Shinomiya is nearby, and injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.31,0:44:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Honju's severed offensive\Nuniorgan has regenerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.31,0:44:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's condensing energy for an attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.27,0:44:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm done for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.06,0:44:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.52,0:44:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.73,0:44:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.31,0:44:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job, Kikoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.31,0:45:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.85,0:45:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you worked so hard,\Neverybody was able to evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.69,0:45:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.77,0:45:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.44,0:45:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.65,0:45:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.19,0:45:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.77,0:45:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.81,0:45:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell\Nthe Defense Force about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.06,0:45:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.06,0:45:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you more in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.56,0:45:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I only need a sec to kick this thing's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.31,0:45:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So just relax and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.48,0:46:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm detecting a mysterious ultra-powerful\Nenergy source near the Honju!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.81,0:46:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a new Kaiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.85,0:46:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.85,0:46:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do we have visual?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.40,0:46:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion knocked out our comms network.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.35,0:46:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not have visual.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.10,0:46:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is this number right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.40,0:46:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortitude 9.8?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.06,0:46:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.35,0:46:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The blast must've scrambled\Nthe measurement system.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.69,0:46:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.81,0:46:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it'd be one of\Nthe most powerful Kaiju in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.73,0:46:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm running out of time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.27,0:46:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm cleaning you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.90,0:46:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with one punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.40,0:47:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.85,0:47:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.31,0:47:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.27,0:47:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.02,0:47:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't put yourself in danger like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.94,0:47:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.19,0:47:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.23,0:47:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran off while my back was turned,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.94,0:47:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and sure enough,\NI find you here, transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.31,0:47:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking maybe I could\Njust transform a part of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.31,0:47:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I saw the Honju\NI was like, "No way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.56,0:47:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.94,0:47:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.77,0:48:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashiro and Hoshina have\Narrived at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.85,0:48:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.73,0:48:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you have to do to cause this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.27,0:48:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.60,0:48:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the operation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.65,0:48:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An additional three examinees\Nhave arrived at Shelter 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.85,0:48:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Kikoru Shinomiya,\NReno Ichikawa, and Kafka Hibino.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.81,0:48:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're safe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.02,0:48:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All examinees are now accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.23,0:48:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.44,0:48:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During a Defense Force\Nselection exam,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.19,0:48:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an unusual incident took place,\Nwith Kaiju suddenly coming back to life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.19,0:48:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Radio
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.40,0:48:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were several injuries during\Nthe incident, but zero fatalities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.52,0:48:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Kaiju that came back to life\Nwere defeated by members{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.35,0:48:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero? Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.90,0:48:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the Third Division\Nwho were present during the exam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.06,0:48:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. No way there were zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.77,0:48:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is one of these\N"Captain" people that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.98,0:48:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaiju No. 8 remains at large,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.56,0:48:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Bureau of Neutralization\Nis enhancing security...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.85,0:48:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 8? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.56,0:49:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... this is how you answer a phone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.94,0:49:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, where've you been?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.65,0:49:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Breaktime's over, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.65,0:49:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.60,0:49:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you "uh" me. Get back here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.10,0:49:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.06,0:49:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.73,0:49:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Humans are so particular about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.31,0:49:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.90,0:49:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bad case of diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.02,0:49:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You had us all worried, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.40,0:49:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell someone where you're going\Nbefore you hole up in the toilets, new kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.60,0:49:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Toku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.81,0:49:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard there was\Nan accident at the exam site.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.60,0:49:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.73,0:49:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.48,0:49:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Kafka and Ichikawa okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.81,0:49:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.06,0:49:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we open it on three.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.19,0:50:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how it turns out,\Nthis is my last shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.10,0:50:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will the path I'm on\Ntake me all the way to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.73,0:50:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to find out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.35,0:50:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.31,0:50:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Examinee Number 2032
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.31,0:50:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.40,0:50:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Examination Results
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.40,0:50:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru Shinomiya will speak\Non behalf of the incoming class!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.31,0:50:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.98,0:50:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The twenty-seven of you are,\Nas of this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.56,0:50:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,officers in the Defense Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.10,0:51:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of all 27 of us, I swear that\Nwe will lay down our lives for the cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.81,0:51:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped a lot during\Nthe incident after the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.19,0:51:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, there were no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.06,0:51:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, you have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.31,0:51:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't me who defeated them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.52,0:51:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kafka Hibino, you should be\Nthe one hearing these words...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.06,0:51:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why aren't you here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.31,0:51:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is humiliating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.90,0:51:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still want some answers\Nfrom you about that Kaiju form, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.81,0:51:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not gonna let you just up\Nand disappear on me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.81,0:51:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.44,0:51:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.23,0:51:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.73,0:51:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 2032. Kafka Hibino. Failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.31,0:51:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He scored the lowest on the fitness exam
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.31,0:51:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and a zero on his aptitude test,\Nso there's not much to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.73,0:51:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds about right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.94,0:52:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.56,0:52:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty, I'll take him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.52,0:52:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, his numbers are below average.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.52,0:52:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not cut out to be an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.02,0:52:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But in actual combat during the last exam,\Nhe was able to locate the enemy's weak points,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.44,0:52:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and he aided the overall effort by prioritizing\Nhelping others over his own kill count.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.31,0:52:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many people are capable of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.77,0:52:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And more than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.40,0:52:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The dude was funny as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.10,0:52:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really all you care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.90,0:52:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if we'll ever\Npromote him to a full officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.81,0:52:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll bring him into my platoon as a\Ncadet and give him some more training.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.27,0:52:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being enrolled as a cadet,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.81,0:52:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had him sit out the induction ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.44,0:52:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Glad to hear it, Kafka Hibino.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.31,0:52:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now that we're all here,\Nlet's have a word from Captain Ashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.85,0:52:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'm glad that you all decided\Nto volunteer for the Defense Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.06,0:53:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,enduring and passing that difficult exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.77,0:53:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.77,0:53:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,These last few years,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.81,0:53:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we've seen far more Kaiju with far\Nhigher fortitudes than was typical before.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.94,0:53:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also now seen this strange incident\Nwhere dead Kaiju came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.15,0:53:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,These neutralization missions\Nwill be extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.98,0:53:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you may die on your very first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.52,0:53:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely no guarantee\Nthat you'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.69,0:53:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so...\NNo, that's exactly {\i1}why{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.35,0:53:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to entrust your lives to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.94,0:53:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to be standing at the very front,\Nacting as both your shield and spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.27,0:53:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.06,0:53:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be standing next to you soon, Mina!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.40,0:53:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.35,0:53:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.31,0:53:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Awkward
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.81,0:53:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.94,0:53:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.19,0:53:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's calling Captain Ashiro by her first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.56,0:53:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.81,0:53:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.81,0:54:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.31,0:54:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke out of turn and\Ndisrespected a superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.98,0:54:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me one hundred push-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.60,0:54:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't mean to say that out loud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.40,0:54:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.56,0:54:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Ashiro, I think you're going\Na little easy on the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.94,0:54:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.19,0:54:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I just see her smile?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.85,0:54:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He just got here, and he's\Nalready bringing the comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.77,0:54:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.94,0:54:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This place can get pretty gloomy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.85,0:54:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.10,0:54:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.56,0:54:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.44,0:54:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.90,0:54:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You really hung in there, old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.44,0:54:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arms tight against your sides, wrists slack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.19,0:54:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let your instincts aim the reticle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.19,0:55:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and don't pull the trigger...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.94,0:55:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Squeeze it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.77,0:55:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Squeeze!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.27,0:55:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Squeeze!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.31,0:55:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reno Ichikawa,\Nfire training exercise complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.90,0:55:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time, 2:35.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.02,0:55:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estimated unleashed combat power, 18%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.40,0:55:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruichi-kun, I've got a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.98,0:55:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm impressed. He's grown\Na lot in a very short time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.60,0:55:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reno set another personal best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.19,0:55:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.10,0:55:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let him beat me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.10,0:55:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iharu Furuhashi, 2:15.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.65,0:55:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estimated unleashed combat power, 20%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.19,0:55:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.56,0:55:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.90,0:55:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky, Reno.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.69,0:55:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.15,0:56:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikoru Shinomiya, 1:16.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.27,0:56:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estimated unleashed combat power, 55%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.98,0:56:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Play nice, kids. Both of your scores\Ncombined are still worse than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.56,0:56:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.69,0:56:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I train, the more she makes me\Nrealize just how average I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.60,0:56:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got time to worry\Nabout people better than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.52,0:56:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My combat power's as good as yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.23,0:56:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got to worry about those above me\N{\i0}and{\i1} those below me, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.27,0:56:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set a new best when it's my turn, Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.06,0:56:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kafka Hibino, 6:39.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.98,0:56:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estimated combat power, 1%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.81,0:56:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.06,0:56:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Kikoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.65,0:56:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally turned that zero into a one!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.56,0:56:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.31,0:56:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Tell me how awesome I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.81,0:56:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting so happy\Nwhen you're 1% and I'm 55%?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.65,0:56:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.69,0:56:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Vice-Captain Hoshina?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.27,0:57:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never gonna be\Na full officer at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.06,0:57:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fired in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.69,0:57:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.77,0:57:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Old dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.44,0:57:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, ten laps around the perimeter\Nand we call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.60,0:57:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.15,0:57:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You complained, so now it's fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.23,0:57:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.15,0:57:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.77,0:57:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The new recruits have quite\Na few rivalries between them already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.15,0:57:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.23,0:57:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like, even when I'm not around,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.94,0:57:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they're competing with each other\Nand making each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.27,0:57:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.90,0:57:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to do laps at the end, too...\NThe vice-captain is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.69,0:57:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you need to build\Nup some more muscle, Reno.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.60,0:57:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, yours aren't that\Nmuch different than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.85,0:57:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fitness eval scores are always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.94,0:57:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? Look at these biceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.06,0:57:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like they're just for show to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.15,0:57:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Reno's more stubborn than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.48,0:57:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit bickering over stupid stuff, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.44,0:58:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the muscles\Nof a hard-working grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.35,0:58:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're getting some bulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.60,0:58:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exhale{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.40,0:58:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bounce{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.40,0:58:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.15,0:58:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be in the Defense\NForce with a spare tire!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.40,0:58:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very rude, Iharu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.27,0:58:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll happen to you too\Nwhen you hit 28 or so!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.90,0:58:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually lost a ton of weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.94,0:58:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.90,0:58:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I challenge you all to arm wrestling!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.98,0:58:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer on!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.27,0:58:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.23,0:58:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me just set a towel down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.94,0:58:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. It's awful noisy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.98,0:58:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.98,0:58:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just talking about\Nhow scrawny we all were.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.10,0:58:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what you'd expect\Nfrom a former military officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.48,0:58:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters isn't your muscles!\NRight, Reno?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.40,0:58:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, it's been a while\Nsince I've done anything like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.27,0:58:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what matters is your results!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.15,0:58:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll outdo you in training tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.69,0:59:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.44,0:59:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have a lot of time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.02,0:59:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to work twice\Nas hard as everybody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.73,0:59:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.19,0:59:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain Hoshina!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.52,0:59:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting your Zs is part of the job too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.48,0:59:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let myself get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.77,0:59:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For Captain Ashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.65,0:59:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.06,0:59:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what you said\Nat the induction ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.65,0:59:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised I'd fight by her side!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.10,0:59:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know I could interpret that as saying\Nyou're going to steal my vice-captain spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.94,0:59:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.02,0:59:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.65,0:59:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I do mean it. I'll do my best\Nto make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.35,1:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.35,1:00:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got two more hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.98,1:00:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off the lights when\Nyou leave and lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.10,1:00:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you have my\Nspot next to Captain Ashiro.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.15,1:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you—
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.94,1:00:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.81,1:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get too close\Nto the rest of the officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.65,1:00:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In this line of work, something could\Nhappen to any one of them at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.52,1:00:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.48,1:00:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a training exercise, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.85,1:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.73,1:00:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. It's time for your first mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.73,1:01:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency Kaiju alert.\NEmergency Kaiju alert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.31,1:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The epicenter is located in Sagamihara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.65,1:01:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Citizens in the surrounding area are asked\Nto follow JSDF orders and evacuate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.94,1:01:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.90,1:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiju Evacuation
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.81,1:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's room on the buses for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.94,1:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All platoons and all JSDF\Nforces are ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.73,1:01:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Ashiro has reached the sniper point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.15,1:01:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lure the Honju to Sector Bravo\Nand provide fire support.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.69,1:01:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.81,1:01:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}JSDF Artillery Regiment Command Post,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.31,1:01:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}now initiating fire support\Nfor the Defense Force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.60,1:02:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for your big debut.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.69,1:02:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Start by showing your superiors\Njust how damn good you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.31,1:02:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.52,1:02:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's not like the exam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.52,1:02:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel strangely calm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.81,1:02:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can tell the suit is helping me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.02,1:02:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unleashing combat power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.90,1:02:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too far out in front!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.27,1:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your combat power is 1%,\Nso stay in the rear!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.94,1:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.65,1:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Two legs down. Finish it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.90,1:02:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Furuhashi!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.98,1:03:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.02,1:03:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that, Reno?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.44,1:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do that by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.23,1:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.23,1:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I swapped out the burst rounds\Nin my gun for freeze rounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.35,1:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a better fit for my style.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.23,1:03:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can slow down the enemy while I fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.27,1:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, once I get the hang of this,\NI'll be even better at hunting Kaiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.69,1:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Our observation teams have verified\Nthat Sector Juliet is clear of Yoju.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.27,1:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All Yoju have been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.81,1:03:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The kill reports keep coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.77,1:03:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.40,1:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ikaruga Platoon will advance,\Nwith Ichikawa and Furuhashi at the forefront.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.73,1:03:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa and Iharu, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.73,1:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.90,1:03:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's working so hard,\Nand I'm just slowing them down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.90,1:03:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there anything I can do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.27,1:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.15,1:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.56,1:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow, even with just 1%,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.35,1:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the suit makes it easy\Nto dismantle their bodies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.98,1:04:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a pretty standard structure\Nfor fungal-type Kaiju,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.06,1:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the core's not where it usually is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.23,1:04:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.56,1:04:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's not here, then maybe over there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.23,1:04:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a second...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.27,1:04:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vice-Captain Hoshina,\NI've located the Yoju core.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.31,1:04:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.23,1:04:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at the base of the neck,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.06,1:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are hard, fibrous muscles on top\Nof it that serve as its backbone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.31,1:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Officers with weaker attack power\Nmight need to hit them from the sides.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.10,1:04:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there's one more thing.\NThis one's important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.56,1:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yoju have reproductive organs too.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.52,1:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The white, bumpy organs near their rears.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.10,1:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't destroy those organs,\Ntheir corpses might spawn new Yoju.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.69,1:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kafka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.31,1:05:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some damn fine work.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.35,1:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okonogi-chan, share that news\Nwith the rest of the team.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.06,1:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.90,1:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharing information on Yoju core\Nand reproductive organs with all officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.19,1:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you picked up some\Nof that at your last job,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.73,1:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I guess your studying really paid off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.77,1:05:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.06,1:05:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I helped the Defense Force!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.69,1:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Honju has reached the designated\Ncombat initiation point.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.40,1:05:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,JSDF ground and air forces\Nare requested to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.85,1:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Target sighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.40,1:05:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Compensation for Coriolis force,\Ngravitational force complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.48,1:05:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No additional targets in area.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.31,1:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One round loaded and ready to fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.44,1:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.40,1:05:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All conditions met for firing to commence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.69,1:05:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are cleared to fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.40,1:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka-kun...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.35,1:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is who I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.90,1:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unleashed combat power, 96%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.52,1:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this one closely, Kafka.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.35,1:06:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.48,1:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the power of the person\Nyou're trying to stand beside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.94,1:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Second round loaded and ready to fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.56,1:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.31,1:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are cleared to fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.10,1:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honju vital signs have disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.69,1:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's collapsing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.40,1:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.90,1:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's totally different from when you look\Nat it on TV or through binoculars!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.56,1:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's incredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.81,1:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.27,1:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.56,1:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yoju inside its body\Nswarm out now that it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.73,1:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys! We're wrapping up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.15,1:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're done cleaning up the riff-raff,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.90,1:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we can all go home\Nand have a yummy breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.98,1:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.40,1:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, as of this moment,\Nyou are no longer a cadet,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.19,1:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but a full-fledged Defense Force officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.44,1:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to give everything\NI have to the fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.73,1:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, I'll be going...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.31,1:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.48,1:08:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a long way from being\Nable to fight by my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.56,1:08:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Mina does remember!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.48,1:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just you wait, Mina!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.15,1:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fifty push-ups for failing\Nto address a superior by their title.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.48,1:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it again!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.19,1:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiju No. 8...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.85,1:09:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and No. 9 need to be discussed at HQ,\Nwhich requires my presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.65,1:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whew...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.10,1:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've put Vice-Captain Hoshina in charge,\Nso ask him about the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.40,1:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.90,1:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And... it was Hoshina who\Nrecommended you for full officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.10,1:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it only happened because\Nof your success in the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.77,1:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The vice-captain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.02,1:09:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Live up to his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.81,1:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.90,1:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him down!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.31,1:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've finally taken the first step!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.81,1:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get some sleep\Nso I can be ready for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.85,1:10:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting rest is part of the job, too...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.02,1:10:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation room, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.23,1:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're seeing dozens of Kaiju inside the base!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.15,1:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears the Kaiju have\Nattacked us from the air!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.31,1:10:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Estimated fortitudes 6.1, 6.3, 6.2, 6.5...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.90,1:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every one of them is...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.81,1:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kaiju!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.85,1:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...Honju class?!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.60,1:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hoshina.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.69,1:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Ashiro is away,\Nso I'll be giving the orders here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.73,1:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's on night watch,\Ntake battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.10,1:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the off-duty officers here, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.35,1:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.98,1:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lure as many as you can into the training area!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.35,1:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make damn sure none of them get off the base!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.31,1:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we're not hearing any reports\Nof damage from outside the base...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.19,1:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That can't mean...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.10,1:11:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they after the base itself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.81,1:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.35,1:11:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyvern-type Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.19,1:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things are bad news...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.98,1:11:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wyvern types?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.81,1:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then... that means something's not right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.73,1:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vice-Captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.02,1:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka! You're still alive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.85,1:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.73,1:12:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's something wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.06,1:12:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You only see about a dozen or so\Nwyvern-type Kaiju each year,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.23,1:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's always something\Nthey have in common.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.31,1:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.40,1:12:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But these guys showed up in a group!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.77,1:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Which can only mean one thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.52,1:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something out there that's got\Nthe power to make them swallow their pride,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.77,1:12:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the intelligence to act\Nwith a goal in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.35,1:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,An incredibly powerful leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.02,1:12:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Target sighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.27,1:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hangin' up, Kafka.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.27,1:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the strongest human at this base?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.56,1:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can speak, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.19,1:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain ain't here,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.77,1:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.56,1:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.44,1:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That settles it, then. You are my prey.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Honju's estimated fortitude\Ncalculations complete!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.81,1:13:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 8.3... That's Daikaiju class!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.81,1:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikaruga, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.15,1:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.94,1:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You command the fight against the Yoju.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.31,1:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Prioritize keeping them in the base\Nand away from civilians,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.19,1:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and keeping the main building online.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.85,1:13:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.81,1:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the Honju, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.94,1:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.27,1:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.15,1:13:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This thing's punches hit like a meteor strike!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.85,1:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One solid hit, and I'm a dead man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.44,1:13:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.23,1:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unharmed?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.31,1:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunners, swap to oscillator rounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.10,1:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't attack from the front!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.77,1:14:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice... Hibino?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.56,1:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to attack their backs...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.56,1:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same type that was reported in '03!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.65,1:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.69,1:14:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The old dude?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.10,1:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The front is easier to hit\Nwhen they're in flight,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.48,1:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the skin's thick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.06,1:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The skin on the back is as thin as possible\Nto help keep their weight down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.52,1:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, Hibino!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.15,1:14:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Split up to run decoy in front\Nwhile hitting the back!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.77,1:14:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.94,1:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the decoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.81,1:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get behind it, Haruichi.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.40,1:14:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me one for this!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.06,1:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.52,1:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Combat power fully unleashed!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.85,1:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.31,1:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Kaiju are working together?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.81,1:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good! We can't get behind them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.65,1:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've failed as well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.73,1:15:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another Kaiju blocked us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.52,1:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do we do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.23,1:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we can't get behind them, then how...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.98,1:15:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's another way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.73,1:15:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.90,1:15:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.19,1:15:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,use my unstoppable power...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.60,1:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to smash right through their front armor!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.23,1:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shinomiya's new weapon?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.35,1:15:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hits pretty hard, for a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.15,1:15:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing I don't like, though,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.44,1:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is that such an ugly weapon doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.94,1:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Squadron-Style Axe Technique\NNumber One: Falling Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.73,1:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Two: Water Skimmer!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.56,1:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.27,1:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Above me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.48,1:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Freeze rounds?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.10,1:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Reno...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.81,1:16:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Shinomiya.\NThey attack from the sky, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.44,1:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.44,1:16:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm impressed he can fight like that\Nagainst Kaiju this strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.02,1:16:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Three: Half Moon!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.69,1:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she get them?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.10,1:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.81,1:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can have the honor of helping me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.98,1:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can keep up, that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.35,1:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.90,1:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, search the battlefield for openings\Nand catch the enemy off guard!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.56,1:17:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.23,1:17:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.52,1:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we need to...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.52,1:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the enemy from behind\Nwhen Shinomiya's got 'em distracted!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.98,1:17:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vice-Captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.44,1:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.94,1:17:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in the training grounds,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.90,1:17:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to worry about\Nhurting the officers if I go all out.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.19,1:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unleashed combat power, 92%!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.06,1:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, time to neutralize this Kaiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.65,1:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.19,1:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't make it in time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.10,1:18:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I just transform part of my body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.81,1:18:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hibino-san?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.52,1:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Minase?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.40,1:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.81,1:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you learned to use your suit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.69,1:18:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I am a full officer,\Nyou know! So of course...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.94,1:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hibino-san, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.44,1:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.52,1:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoru!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.90,1:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.94,1:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reno and I will distract the Kaiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.52,1:18:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the wounded out of here while we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.27,1:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.56,1:19:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.06,1:19:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't take any risks, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.69,1:19:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a full officer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.44,1:19:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in your fellow officers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.98,1:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.15,1:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.48,1:19:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did they learn to work together like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.44,1:19:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Report! Nakanoshima's unit has arrived!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.15,1:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ikaruga!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.23,1:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebina's unit has arrived as well and is\Nheading to assist in the southern quadrant!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.85,1:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought you could get away with this,\Nhuh, you damn Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.90,1:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The senior officers who were off duty?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.85,1:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They came to help!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.35,1:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Takao Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.15,1:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attack the Yoju in the air\Nwith freeze rounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.98,1:19:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Itakura Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.69,1:19:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've secured the warehouse area.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.94,1:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're starting to push them back,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.10,1:19:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,even without the captain here!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.23,1:19:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna win this fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.56,1:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.48,1:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slicing right through\Nthe tiny gaps in my exoskeleton.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.48,1:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.77,1:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know exactly what\Nyou're aiming for, it's easy for me to...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.02,1:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,handle it...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.02,1:20:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshina-Style Sword-Slay Technique\NNumber Two: Cross Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.19,1:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Four: Wild Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.81,1:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So aiming for the gaps was just a diversion?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.44,1:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is how a fight should be!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.06,1:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A head-on battle against an opponent\Nwhose strength rivals your own!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.60,1:20:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rivals! Rivals! Rivals! Rivals!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.19,1:21:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.77,1:21:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your core's a lot smaller than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.98,1:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Six:
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.19,1:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eightfold Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.48,1:21:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.35,1:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the vice-captain for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.85,1:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that, Kaiju?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.94,1:21:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.27,1:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.81,1:21:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vice-Captain?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.23,1:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hibino-san?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.23,1:21:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It got bigger?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.06,1:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The position of its core shifted,\Nso I wasn't able to fully destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.23,1:22:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Its fortitude is rising alongside the heat...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.19,1:22:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.81,1:22:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortitude...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.15,1:22:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,9.0!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.10,1:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's massive...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.06,1:22:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The vice-captain can't handle\Nsomething that size by himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.85,1:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Three: Return Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.15,1:22:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your speed won't save you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.40,1:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible. He's still fighting it,\Neven after it transformed. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.65,1:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My blades aren't cutting all the way through!\NThis is why I hate giant Kaiju!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.35,1:23:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exceeding operational limits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.60,1:23:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cancel maximum release immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.06,1:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm overheating?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.81,1:23:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ten minutes\Nsince your maximum release!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.60,1:23:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.56,1:23:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-destructed?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.81,1:23:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's just like a Kaiju.\NTotally cold-blooded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.15,1:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're like living missiles!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.60,1:23:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.94,1:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It gave me a nice smoke screen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.69,1:23:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Six!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.56,1:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Limit exceeded. Canceling maximum release.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.10,1:24:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seek medical treatment immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.27,1:24:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vice-Captain! Vice-Captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.98,1:24:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.44,1:24:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry... I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.77,1:24:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.56,1:24:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my shields set to max...\NThat Kaiju hits like a truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.35,1:24:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost my maximum release.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.44,1:24:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So what now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.44,1:24:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.52,1:24:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'd better keep\Nfighting till the end, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.27,1:24:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you can't fight like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.60,1:24:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshina-Style Sword-Slay Technique\NNumber One: Air Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.65,1:24:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.56,1:24:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't defeat me with those weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.60,1:25:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she told me something else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.77,1:25:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time for me to shoot my foe,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.31,1:25:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will you clear a path for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.15,1:25:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She left me in charge of the base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.19,1:25:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll protect it if it kills me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.65,1:25:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.81,1:25:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.31,1:25:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.69,1:25:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.27,1:25:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Ichikawa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.19,1:25:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My comrades' lives are more important!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.90,1:25:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great work, everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.69,1:25:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.81,1:25:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.02,1:25:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I win this fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.10,1:26:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the vice-captain of the base.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.81,1:26:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My job's to pass the baton to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.60,1:26:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okonogi. This is an emergency,\Nso I'm skipping the procedures.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.48,1:26:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, ma'am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.44,1:26:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to blow this thing up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.56,1:26:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to make you my vice-captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.56,1:26:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unleashed combat power, 96%.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.98,1:26:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for me to shoot my foe.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.23,1:27:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Honju is down!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.81,1:27:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.15,1:27:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.77,1:27:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.27,1:27:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Captain Ashiro for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.65,1:27:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.44,1:27:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Defense Force\NI've wanted to be in since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.10,1:27:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cool...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.40,1:27:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stand right there\Nwith them someday...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.06,1:27:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.02,1:27:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How can you say that when\NI'm having an emotional moment?!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.44,1:27:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a heart of stone!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.94,1:27:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.56,1:27:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.90,1:27:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.73,1:28:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain and I will deal with the Yoju.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.56,1:28:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.60,1:28:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.52,1:28:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the Yoju to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.19,1:28:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.48,1:28:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.73,1:28:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yoju...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.73,1:28:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that last scream wasn't its death rattle?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.31,1:28:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy levels rising...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.52,1:28:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ultra-massive Yoju bomb!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.06,1:28:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The blast's estimated impact\Nis equal to 20 kilotons of TNT!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.19,1:28:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same as a nuclear bomb!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.85,1:28:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.60,1:28:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.31,1:29:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... there's no time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.94,1:29:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that thing hits the ground...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.31,1:29:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Human...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.90,1:29:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this fight is a draw.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.31,1:29:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.23,1:29:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka?!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.77,1:29:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here! There's nothing you can do!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.52,1:29:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.69,1:29:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How's he so fast?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.56,1:29:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not what 1% unleashed\Ncombat power looks like!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.31,1:29:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're detecting a gigantic\NKaiju signal above the base!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.15,1:29:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortitude 9.8!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.94,1:29:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This signal, it's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.10,1:30:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaiju No. 8!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.10,1:30:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Ichikawa.\NI don't think I can keep my promise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.73,1:30:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a long way from being\Nable to fight by my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.10,1:30:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mina... I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.81,1:30:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.48,1:30:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.52,1:30:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.73,1:30:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone else risked their\Nlives during this fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.52,1:30:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't be the only one\Nwho puts his own safety first!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.85,1:30:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm part of the Defense Force, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.52,1:30:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an officer of the Third Division, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.40,1:30:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.10,1:31:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, on the ground!\NShields at max!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.31,1:32:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, now I've done it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.98,1:32:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My arms and legs\Nare barely holding together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.52,1:32:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm too old to be pulling stunts like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.60,1:32:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.27,1:32:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.40,1:32:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiju No. 8.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.77,1:32:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you into custody.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.06,1:33:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kafka Hibino.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.81,1:33:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In accordance with Article 13\Nof the Defense Force Code,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.81,1:33:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you are to be transferred\Nto the Ariake Maritime Base.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.40,1:33:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To ensure the safety of the citizenry—
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.77,1:33:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.85,1:34:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I still... try to stand by your side?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.73,1:34:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.98,1:34:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.48,1:34:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.35,1:34:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Defense Force, salute!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.69,1:37:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez... are you okay, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.31,1:37:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you eat\Nuntil you got sick like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.98,1:37:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about the track and field\Nmeet we have this weekend and got nervous...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.44,1:37:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people stop eating\Nwhen they get nervous!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.15,1:38:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.56,1:38:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. I bought you a bunch of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.94,1:38:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some water?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.40,1:38:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not planning on solving your\Nstomach troubles by becoming a Kaiju, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.19,1:38:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,9:30 AM
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.06,1:38:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.31,1:38:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for Senpai, but it's\Nthe perfect day to be off duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.94,1:38:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So you and Reno are off tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.69,1:38:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Previous Day
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.52,1:38:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. You too, Iharu?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.52,1:38:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people in our class have\Nthe same day off.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.69,1:38:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.56,1:38:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.31,1:38:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.15,1:39:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask somebody to go with you, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.85,1:39:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.15,1:39:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Soshiro Hoshina
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.90,1:39:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Vice-Captain Hoshina is off, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.69,1:39:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's rare.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.69,1:39:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay...  I've actually got\Nthe whole day off for once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.10,1:39:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to enjoy it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.81,1:39:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to make today a great day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.31,1:39:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I am doing my\Ndaily weight training!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.56,1:39:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even think about it!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.02,1:39:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do you spend days off, again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.90,1:39:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's everybody doing, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.85,1:40:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Ichikawa, you don't know\Nhow to spend your days off?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.27,1:40:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're young. You need to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.90,1:40:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I'll show you the fun ways\Nto spend your off time in Tachikawa.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.48,1:40:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you going somewhere\Ntoday, Vice-Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.23,1:40:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.48,1:40:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got somewhere to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.27,1:40:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Reno? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.81,1:40:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Iharu-kun? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.40,1:40:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Was gonna tune up my ride.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.15,1:40:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, were you talking\Nabout something with the vice-captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.19,1:40:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.23,1:40:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seemed like he was\Ndoing something important.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.65,1:40:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a mysterious guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.52,1:40:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean when\Nhe said he had somewhere to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.69,1:40:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a lady!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.56,1:40:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it didn't feel like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.31,1:40:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she's like!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.19,1:40:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she pretty?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.02,1:40:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.60,1:41:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... that tense air about him...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.35,1:41:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! He must be doing\Nextra training on his day off!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.27,1:41:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's so strong—
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.23,1:41:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He's a man too after all!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.27,1:41:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer! I'll give you a good petting!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.35,1:41:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just your type, Iharu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.19,1:41:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's the kind of guy who'd...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.15,1:41:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's allowed to fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.27,1:41:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he is, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.44,1:41:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think that's it!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.77,1:41:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today, at least...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.02,1:41:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to bet, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.56,1:41:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Loser buys dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.31,1:41:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.77,1:41:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Iharu-kun, this is a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.35,1:42:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to settle the bet!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.44,1:42:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't be tailing the vice-captain...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.94,1:42:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If he finds us, we're in\Nfor a lot worse than a lecture!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.65,1:42:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't find out! We've got our helmets on!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.90,1:42:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sounds fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.65,1:42:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.60,1:42:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't doing anything anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.65,1:42:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He knew...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.73,1:42:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! He's going into the parking lot!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.23,1:42:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hokkaido Products Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.15,1:42:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.44,1:42:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.40,1:42:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.60,1:42:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Try a free sample!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.02,1:42:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission complete, Captain Ashiro.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.35,1:42:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have attained the limited-run\Ntop-quality dried squid snacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.40,1:42:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}{\i1}Ezo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.15,1:42:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.23,1:42:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done as always, Hoshina.\NYou have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.44,1:42:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dried squid?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.90,1:42:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well, that sucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.77,1:42:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was on an errand\Nfor Captain Ashiro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.65,1:43:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of jealous...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.65,1:43:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two weird guys over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.31,1:43:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.72,1:43:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you lost the bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.02,1:43:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.73,1:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.48,1:43:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "a lady"!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.94,1:43:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I win, just barely.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.65,1:43:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A lady, sure, but she's his boss!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.81,1:43:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.73,1:43:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.81,1:43:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask you to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.15,1:43:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while\Nsince you've had a day off.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.98,1:43:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was on the way to where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.60,1:43:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.35,1:43:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.94,1:43:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.06,1:43:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I'm excited for this...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.77,1:43:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But time to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.98,1:43:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is his real destination?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.81,1:43:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The bet's not over!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.65,1:43:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Reno!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.69,1:43:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.90,1:43:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.27,1:44:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's stopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.31,1:44:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We could just walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.56,1:44:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.60,1:44:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain Hoshina!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.56,1:44:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we have a reservation for lunch,\Nbut we're running late.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.60,1:44:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get a taxi to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.69,1:44:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.56,1:44:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we couldn't ask you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.77,1:44:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! Hop in!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.40,1:44:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.77,1:44:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.52,1:44:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.19,1:44:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.02,1:44:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.06,1:44:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.48,1:44:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're on the reservation list, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.23,1:44:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.10,1:45:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.44,1:45:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a nice design,\Nso it'd go well with the fire grill.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.44,1:45:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this should give\Nthe place some atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.19,1:45:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.23,1:45:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that strong, or that functional.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.69,1:45:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't carry it in a backpack either.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.77,1:45:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You might end up having to\Ncarry it for days at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.65,1:45:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be ready to survive\Neven the harshest circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.02,1:45:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're imagining\Nsomething totally different.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.02,1:45:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a second?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.73,1:45:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.31,1:45:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.90,1:45:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So yeah, buy an older model for cheap.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.60,1:45:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They go for about this much.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.31,1:45:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I see!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.81,1:46:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.44,1:46:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck bargain-hunting.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.90,1:46:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.40,1:46:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take your order?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.48,1:46:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.85,1:47:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not really getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.23,1:47:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.90,1:47:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to find out\Nwhat it is he's doing!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.81,1:47:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.69,1:47:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.90,1:47:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get\Nthat surprised, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.31,1:47:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And Minase-san and Igarashi-san...\Nwhat a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.15,1:47:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We all went out to lunch!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.19,1:47:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And get this!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.23,1:47:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think drove us to the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.35,1:47:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hint is...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.65,1:47:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, we know the answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.56,1:47:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tailing Vice-Captain Hoshina?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.15,1:48:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Poking into someone's\Nprivate life like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.23,1:48:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In America you'd get sued!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.56,1:48:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys are such idiots.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.44,1:48:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Kafka Hibino?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.77,1:48:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's off today too, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.60,1:48:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got a good grasp of his schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.56,1:48:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you hoping to see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.40,1:48:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.40,1:48:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that it was nice not to\Nhave him sweating up the place on my day off!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.69,1:48:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.90,1:48:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,More people!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.56,1:48:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tailing the vice-captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.15,1:48:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised. I didn't think you\Nwere the type, Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.40,1:48:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I would never...!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.19,1:48:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Shh! He'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.98,1:48:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never be so vulgar!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.31,1:48:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.44,1:49:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody saw you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.31,1:49:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.52,1:49:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the type that stands out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.98,1:49:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarcastic asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.73,1:49:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's the stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.02,1:49:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.81,1:49:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.98,1:49:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy's huge!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.23,1:49:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.60,1:49:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going on ahead, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.60,1:49:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You come at the designated time.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.52,1:49:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet at the rendezvous spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.15,1:49:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.06,1:49:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of scared...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.56,1:49:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calm down, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.77,1:50:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That case...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.77,1:50:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like the ones we use\Nto transport equipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.44,1:50:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's selling stuff\Non the black market...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.40,1:50:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The black market?!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.73,1:50:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more Kaiju have been showing up,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.85,1:50:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which means more money\Nis needed to fund our defenses.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.44,1:50:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What we just saw was...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.27,1:50:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,him selling weapons to the underworld\Nto get the money we need.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.48,1:50:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.48,1:50:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the vice-captain's one\Nperson who would never do that,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.56,1:50:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so there must be another reason...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.31,1:50:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.73,1:50:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing the dirty work all alone\Nso we don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.44,1:50:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop him, even if I have\Nto punch him in the face!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.27,1:50:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.40,1:50:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Corruption is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.31,1:50:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Defense Force is a symbol of justice!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.69,1:50:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make him realize this is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.81,1:50:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.15,1:50:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Shinomiya, Reno,\Ndon't tell me you're agreeing with them!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.65,1:51:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.23,1:51:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I could count on you, Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.77,1:51:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad somebody agrees with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.77,1:51:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, he needs\Nto be punished appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.06,1:51:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we need to see\Nif it's true, Haruichi.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.19,1:51:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.48,1:51:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.77,1:51:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He drove off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.10,1:51:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunt for him!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.85,1:51:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.31,1:51:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other suspicious buildings\Nor abandoned warehouses around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.94,1:51:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the vice-captain\Nwill become a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.23,1:51:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No... If it's true, he's already a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.15,1:51:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think it's true, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.15,1:51:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.94,1:52:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.94,1:52:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the handover, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.60,1:52:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.40,1:52:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.90,1:52:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me so sad and angry!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.52,1:52:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... If you've seen it,\Nthen I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.85,1:52:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.35,1:52:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.19,1:52:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.98,1:52:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... stop this!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.60,1:52:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain Hoshina!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.31,1:52:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really him!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.02,1:52:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.69,1:52:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.73,1:52:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's cute!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.23,1:52:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what you were doing...?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.65,1:53:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachikawa Disaster Prevention Center
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.35,1:53:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot possibly thank\Nyou enough, Hoshina-san!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.56,1:53:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The star of our show is the\N"Mina Ashiro Sniper Experience," but...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.60,1:53:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen these before!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.65,1:53:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks to you, we've finally\Nfinished our new virtual Soshiro Hoshina!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.23,1:53:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And our permanent exhibit, as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.52,1:53:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to your kindness in donating\Nthose old weapons you don't use anymore!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.90,1:53:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you could just put your\Nautograph on the wall like I asked...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.06,1:53:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.56,1:53:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm pretending to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.15,1:53:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a star, though!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.85,1:53:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and sign the wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.44,1:53:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the new recruits this term, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.73,1:53:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.90,1:53:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know us?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.27,1:53:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you in\Nthe Defense Force newsletter.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.81,1:53:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets sent out to former members.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.40,1:54:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be in the Third Division.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.98,1:54:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I serve as the vice-president\Nof this Disaster Prevention Center.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.65,1:54:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.06,1:54:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.44,1:54:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.69,1:54:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it together!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.35,1:54:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's the vice-captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.02,1:54:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're from a day care in the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.27,1:54:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We invited them for a private opening\Nof the renovated exhibits.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.48,1:54:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.40,1:54:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,These men and women will show you\Nhow to play with the exhibits!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.98,1:54:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask them anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.23,1:54:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.23,1:54:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.52,1:54:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.69,1:54:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.77,1:54:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it up to the top!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.06,1:54:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.06,1:55:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.15,1:55:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.27,1:55:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Herbal Medicine
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.65,1:55:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chinese medicine that'll\Nheal any stomach problems instantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.35,1:55:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This brand's stuff works great.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.23,1:55:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this to Kafka.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.69,1:55:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.06,1:55:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.85,1:55:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He ate too much last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.65,1:55:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So he couldn't come with you today.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.98,1:55:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured he's probably lying in his room.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.31,1:55:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where'd you buy this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.48,1:55:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The department store.\NWhile I was getting those snacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.31,1:55:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He saw us right at the start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.69,1:55:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really is a scary man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.19,1:55:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad this place is popular.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.56,1:55:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps us, because people learn\Nabout the Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.69,1:55:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And this might be\Nwhere we get our new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.35,1:55:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But our ideal is...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.60,1:55:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that when they're grown up,\Nnobody will need the Defense Force anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.02,1:56:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.23,1:56:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your juniors are working\Nhard towards that goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.94,1:56:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency Kaiju alert!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.19,1:56:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency Kaiju alert!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.69,1:56:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Kaiju has appeared in Chofu City.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.77,1:56:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fortitude 3.8.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.40,1:56:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its speed is extremely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.27,1:56:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case, I'll get the kids to safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.65,1:56:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The JSDF is presently evacuating citizens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.65,1:56:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, everyone! It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.27,1:56:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.52,1:56:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go beat up the scary Kaiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.06,1:56:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll be cheering us on.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.69,1:56:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.27,1:56:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going, Hoshina?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.02,1:56:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.31,1:56:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-Captain, we'll provide support!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.77,1:56:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.56,1:56:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Its fortitude isn't that high.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.90,1:57:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not on the team that's\Nsupposed to respond to emergencies today...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.60,1:57:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.98,1:57:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all a bunch of workaholics.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.77,1:57:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if I may...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.15,1:57:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wearing your suit under your outfit.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.19,1:57:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy who doesn't\Nknow how to take a day off.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.98,1:57:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to tease\Nyour superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.98,1:57:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.85,1:57:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.06,1:57:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.40,1:57:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.27,1:57:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.56,1:59:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshina...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.02,1:59:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really appreciate what you did today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.77,1:59:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the way,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.90,1:59:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}why did you suddenly change the handover\Npoint for the weapons and equipment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.81,1:59:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I saw them following me,\Nso I decided to play a little prank.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.44,1:59:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly did make\Nfor an interesting day off.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.90,1:59:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hokkaido Milk Coffee
